getEeuBatch(uint256).details: Returns an EEU batch by ID

getEeuMintedCount().details: Returns the global no. of EEUs minted

getKgCarbonBurned().details: Returns the global no. of KGs carbon burned in EEUs

getKgCarbonMinted().details: Returns the global no. of KGs carbon minted in EEUs

getLedgerEntry(address).details: Returns the _ledger entry for an account

params.batchOwner: who to assign the minted EEUs to
params.qtyEeus: quantity of EEUs in the batch
params.qtyKG: KG quanity of carbon to mint across the EEUs

burnEeus(address,uint8,int256).notice: burns carbons by resizing EEUs, and/or removing EEUs from the _ledger. removes EEUs (or fractions thereof) from the main list and from the _ledger, resizing as necessary. the supplied _ledger owner must hold the supplied quantity of carbon in aggregate across _ledger EEUs, and of the supplied type.

mintEeuBatch(uint8,int256,int256,address.notice: mint and assign ownership new EEU batch
